# <%= projectName %>

<%= description %>

## Setup

Pré-requisitos: Node <%= nodeVersion %>+, npm.

```bash
git clone <repo>
cd <%= projectSlug %>
cp .env.example .env       # preencha segredos reais
npm install
npm run dev
```

